stories.text:
Hi, every one, As the title suggest, I am a react native developer and I wanted to get a job at FAANG.

From various resources, I’ve come to know that at the starting of career, joining at FAANG may not be a good idea.

So, My initial plan is try get selected for internship at siliconvalleyinternship.com/ after spending there 2 years then go for FAANG.

But, Life may not go according to plan. So, I am trying for both.

According to my research, I’ve to be good at what I am doing, in my case it will JavaScript, and Design implementation. I also have be good at Data Structure and Algorithm

Little Bit about myself: Top 8% ( 458 reputation ) in Stack Overflow in 2021 ( https://stackoverflow.com/users/14302873/mrpmohiburrahman ) I am working as a React Native Developer since 30th December, 2020. I do not have any kind project to show case I am willing to work with anything as long as it’s Functional Programming with JS. This is my LinkedIn profile: https://www.linkedin.com/in/mrpmohiburrahman/

What do you suggest? How can I prepare myself so that I’ll be able to join FAANG as a Front End developer or as JS developer on any stack?
stories.title: Ask HN: As a React Native Developer how should one prepare one self for FAANG?
